    <p>Live Tor Experiment PredicTor Improved Performance</p>
    <p>11% compared to Vanilla  6% compared to CAR  Over 1.0s in the 90th.  SB-9 and SB-15 performed the</p>
    <p>slowest.</p>
  </div>
